{"tid":352003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"興德學校涉「影子學生」騙津貼　消息指重案組調查","createTime":"2017-08-08T13:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T07:52:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d904cc120e73bcb2bf8bc45ff26c5ba34dacbe7a","tid":352003,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"屯門興德學校被指以「影子學生」增加學生數目，騙取教育局津貼。消息指，警方6月底接獲教育局轉介，懷疑有人在事件中使用虛假文書，屯門重案組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n有學校的前老師透露，「影子學生」是雙非學童，曾經註冊，但無上課；又指校長曾要求課程主任向教育局提供假資料。<br />\n<br />\n興德學校管理層開記者會，反駁指控無理，並非事實。校長承認有學生請假，但並非全年沒上學，對批評感到委屈，認為指控無根據，已交律師處理。"},{"pid":"6fcc9002e0b20033abcf9681e7f8a90e449ae685","tid":352003,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"香港各行各業都有用大陸人頭呃呢呃路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fa478d21d719ebe6574135c3111739bce3f309","tid":352003,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"慶祝自己好返 西餅費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想笑能死人咩"},{"pid":"4ae89411c880bca2f1e69c7e2bbace7864ce774b","tid":352003,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"咩學生請左假<br />\n請左幾多日<br />\n因乜事請"},{"pid":"65bb1c1edb6510b9f7d053774ec2fd4168e5bf26","tid":352003,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩學生請左假<br />\n請左幾多日<br />\n因乜事請</blockquote><br />\n幾十個學生冇出現過<br />\n校長話正常請假"},{"pid":"32e448afcf5c2b5e9b1fa7571f1682b246b7e7a3","tid":352003,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91558be25bfd39d84fc2b46c1cb6627ac3629eb","tid":352003,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c4588b4bc1d9d275dc59438a13e8c898ab77e8a"